<varlistentry id="options.ForceSize">
	<term>ForceSize <emphasis remap='I'>Size</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>If specified, will force pixmaps to Size instead of the default
		of 64x64. This has no effect on the Size of the displayed icons (they will be croped if larger).</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
